text: Universal High is the second studio album by English band Childhood. It was released on 21 July 2017 under Marathon Artists. ==Critical reception== Universal High was met with generally favourable reviews from critics. At Metacritic, which assigns a weighted average rating out of 100 to reviews from mainstream publications, this release received an average score of 74, based on 14 reviews. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2017 albums Category:Marathon Artists albums
